      <longTitle currentId="idp17824">
        <p>Prohibit the use of wild animals in circuses; and for connected purposes.</p>
      </longTitle>
    </preface>
    <preamble>
      <formula name="EnactingText" currentId="idp20144">
        <p>B<span style="font-variant:small-caps">e it enacted</span> by the Queen’s most Excellent Majesty, by and with the advice and <eol/>consent of the Lords Spiritual and Temporal, and Commons, in this present <eol/>Parliament assembled, and by the authority of the same, as follows:—</p>
      </formula>
